data.text:
Pupri, Bihar, India

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 26.469870, 85.697411.

Pupri is a sub-divisional town of Sitamarhi district in Bihar state, India. The town is situated quite close to the border of India with Nepal and is a small commercial / transportation spot, and a part of Sitamarhi district. It is possible to reach the town by roads or by taking a train at a Janakpur Rail road line.
